title: Lithuania boss Edgaras Jankauskas learnt how to slay gaints from Jose Mourinho… and now he has England in his sights
text:
EFL Special Memories Lithuania boss Edgaras Jankauskas learnt how to slay gaints from Jose Mourinho… and now he has England in his sights 
Jankauskas was in Mourinho’s all-conquering Porto squads, who won the Champions League in 2004 and Uefa Cup in 2003 against the odds Exclusive
